<facsimile><graphic url="https://www.e-manuscripta.ch/i3f/v20/1038278/manifest"/></facsimile><text><body><div type="letter">
<pb facs="1038279" n="125r"/>
<opener>
<lb/>Viro Clarissimo et Excellentissimo 
         <lb/><rs key="pers_DE-588-102552517" type="person">Petro Antonio Michelotti</rs>
<lb/><abbr>S. P. D.</abbr>
<lb/><abbr><rs key="pers_DE-588-119166895" type="person">N. B.</rs></abbr>
</opener>
<p>
<del><lb/>Su<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>a Tibi et <abbr>Clariss.<hi rend="sup">o</hi></abbr> Abbati Fardell<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> me debentur
         <lb/>grati<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>, pro su<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>o quo me prosequimini favore, dum uterque
            <lb/>enixissimo studio id<add> continuo</add> agitis qpud <abbr>Ill<hi rend="sup">mos</hi></abbr> et <abbr>Excell<hi rend="sup">mos</hi></abbr> Studii
         <lb/>Patavini Moderatores, ut ad Cathedram Mathameticam in
         <lb/>Illustri <gap/> Arch<subst><del>y</del><add>i</add></subst>lyceo promovear. Cumque <unclear>exliteris vestris</unclear>
<lb/>humanissimis perspiciam co<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>endationes vestras tantum pondus
         <lb/>habere apud Proceres Vestros</del>
<lb/>Ex <rs key="B_1714-01-24_991170517055305501" type="letter">Literis</rs><note type="editorial">Brief von Pietro Antonio Michelotti an Nicolaus I Bernoulli von 1714.01.14</note> Tuis ut et <choice><sic>Clarisimi</sic><corr>Clarissimi</corr></choice> Abbatis <rs key="pers_DE-588-119291967" type="person">Fardell<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs> <rs key="B_1713-11-26_991170517059105501" type="letter">huma<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>nissimis</rs><note type="editorial">Brief von Michelangelo Fardella an Nicolaus I Bernoulli von 1713.11.26</note><del>cum vel</del> denuo perspexi, quam magno studio <add>et fervore</add><!-- et fervore wurde eingefügt, mit Fritz kontrollieren -->
<lb/>continue agatis<del> ut</del> apud <abbr>Illmos</abbr> et <abbr>Excellmos</abbr> Studii 
         <lb/><rs type="organisation">Patavini</rs><rs key="pers_DE-588-1111043582 pers_DE-588-1178371670 pers_DE-588-1089585993" type="persons">Moderatores</rs><note type="editorial">Von 14.10.1713-7.03.1714 waren die Moderatoren der Universität Padua Alvise Pisani (1664-1741), Francesco Loredan (1656-1715), Giovan Francesco  Morosini (1658-1739)</note>, ut at Cathedram Mathematicam
         <lb/>in illustri isto <rs type="organisation">Archilyc<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>o</rs> promovear, et quam benigne 
         <lb/>co<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>endationes Vestr<unclear>as</unclear> <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> <subst><del>l Illustrissmis</del><add>Nobilissimis</add></subst> Vestris Proceribus 
         <lb/>except<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> fuerint, ita ut non exigua spes sit <del>obtinendi</del>
<lb/><del>spartam hanc illustrem</del> optatum fore negotii hujus exitum<supplied>.</supplied>
<lb/>Officii mei idcirco fuisset cita responsione <add>gratiarum actionem repetere</add>, animumque <subst><del>gratum<gap/></del><add>tanti vestri beneficii</add></subst> me<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>morem demonstrare, sed debiti hujus mei 
         <lb/>exsolutionem<add> cujus rei veniam enixe peto</add> invitus hucusque distuli partim ob negotia, partim ob id 
         <lb/>quod vacuas ad Te venire literas nolebam, 
         <lb/><del>destitutas </del>nullam nempe Problematis mihi propositi solutione<subst><del>s</del><add>m</add></subst> continentes. 
         <pb facs="1038280" n="125v"/>
<lb/><del>I</del><gap/>Deprehendi hoc Problema multum difficultatis habere, et destitutum 
         <lb/>esse variis conditionibus ad ejus solutionem necessariis. Nihil enim dixisti 
         <lb/><add>de his,</add> num gravitas liquidi in quovis canalis positu in considerationem venire 
         <lb/>debeat, num ipsorum vasorum aut canalium elasticitas, num pressiones 
         <lb/>extern<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>, aut num canalis solidus et latera ejus minime cedentia fingi 
         <lb/>possint <abbr><choice><orig><g ref="#etlig">&amp;</g></orig><reg>et</reg></choice>c.</abbr> Quod si tibi placuerit Problema mihi mittere <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> Physicis 
         <lb/>conditionibus liberum et ad pure Mathematicum reductum, tentabo 
         <lb/>num desiderio tuo aliqua ex parte satisfacere potero. Hactenus 
         <lb/>huic Problemati ex condigno incumbere non potui, quia aliis et 
         <lb/>quidem maxime diversis nunc teneor studiis. Vacua enim est ab aliquo 
         <lb/>tempore in nostra Academia Professio Juridica, pro qua adipiscen<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>da moris est ut Disputationibus Publicis Competitores specimina 
         <lb/>qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>dam exhibeant, inter <subst><del>hos</del><add>quos</add></subst> cum et ego nomen licet non serio sed 
         <lb/>exercitii <add>duntaxat</add> gratia professus fuerim, disputandi atque opponendi 
         <lb/>vices semel <add>atque</add> iterum mihi sustinend<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> sunt. Theorema hoc, quod flui<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>da qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>cunque continentibus quibuscunque contenta pressiones 
         <lb/>suas continentibus<del> sine</del> secundum lineas continentium superficiebus 
         <lb/>perpendiculares co<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>unic<choice><orig><g ref="#en">ē</g></orig><reg>en</reg></choice>t, demonstrari ita facile potest: Consideretur 
         <lb/>fluidum <add>ut</add> compositum ex permultis globulis perexiguis, liquet unum<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>quemque globulum pellere <add>vel premere</add> superficiem continentem secundum lineam 
         <lb/>qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> transit per centrum globuli et punctum contactus, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> linea 
         <lb/>semper perpendicularis est superficiei globulum contingenti. Vel sic:
         <lb/><figure facs="1038280_01.png" hand="pers_DE-588-119166895"/>Sit Superficies continens qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>cunque <formula>ABCDEF</formula>, globulus <formula>G</formula> pars fluidi 
         <lb/>contenti, cujus directio qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>cunque 
         <lb/>sit secundum rectam <formula>GD</formula>; <unclear>J</unclear>am vis urgens globulum 
         <pb facs="1038282" n="126r"/>
<lb/>secundum <formula>GD</formula>, resolvi potest in duas alias vires urgentes secundum rectas 
         <lb/><formula>GC</formula> et <formula>GH</formula>, quarum illa perpendicularis h<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>c parallela sit superficiei <formula>BCD</formula>
<lb/>globulum <formula>G</formula> tangenti; patet autem solam vim perpendicularem secundum 
         <lb/><formula>GC</formula> vim suam <choice><sic>exerere</sic><corr>exercere</corr></choice> in superficiem <formula>BCD</formula>, parallelam autem <formula>GH</formula> totam 
         <lb/>absumi suffulciendo globulos contiguos. Cumque idem de omnibus globu<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>lis continentem superficiem contingentibus dici possit, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>cunque 
         <lb/>ipsorum directio fuerit, liquet superficiem continentem in omnibus 
         <lb/>sui punctis a fluido contento perpendiculariter premi. Gloriam 
         <lb/>scriptis <add>aut dissertationibus</add> in publicum editis qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>rere hactenus non stud<unclear>ui</unclear>, cum discenti<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>bus potius quam docentibus me aggregare maluerim observans 
         <lb/>multa s<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>pe ab incauta juventute in publicum deproperari, 
         <lb/>qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> postea <subst><del>cum</del><add>cum</add></subst> <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>tas meliora docuit nollemus esse edita. 
         <lb/><rs key="biblio_ME943KC7" type="biblio">Dissertationem</rs> quidem <add>Iuridico Mathematicam</add> <abbr>A.<hi rend="sup">o</hi></abbr> 1709<choice><orig><g ref="#ndot">.</g></orig><reg></reg></choice> pro Gradu Iuridico edidi 
         <lb/>de Usu Artis Conjectandi in Iure, <subst><del>ubi</del><add>sed</add></subst> illa res leviculas continet, 
         <lb/>memini tamen <subst><del>illam</del><add>eam</add></subst> ab Illustrim<subst><del>ae</del><add>o</add></subst> Reip<del>b</del>ubl. Vestr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> <rs key="pers_DE-588-1236435125" type="person">Residente</rs><note type="editorial">Savioni, Francesco, venezianischer Resident in Zürich von 1711-1714.</note>,
         <lb/><del>qui</del> <del><gap/></del> <add>qui</add> tum temporis Tiguri<del> agenti</del> agebat valde probatam fuisse.
         <lb/>Ejus Exemplar una cum <rs key="biblio_WPXENY2H" type="biblio">Tractatu</rs><del> Def.</del> Posthumo Def. <rs key="pers_DE-588-118509950" type="person">Patrui</rs>
<lb/>quamprimum ad Te mitti curabo.<del>Extant etiam</del> Impressit etiam
         <lb/>nuper <add>Parisiis</add> plurimas <rs key="biblio_QUAQJMHS" type="biblio">epistolas</rs> meas <rs key="pers_DE-588-117601020" type="person">Auctor</rs><note type="editorial">Montmort, Pierre Rémond de (1678-1719). Zweite Edition: Pierre Remond de Montmort, Essay d'Analyse sur les Jeux de Hazard. Seconde Edition. Paris MDCCXIII.</note> <rs key="biblio_69NKSR46" type="biblio">Libri Gallici Essai d'Analyse
            <lb/>sur les jeux de Hazard additas secund<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> hujus Libri editioni</rs><del><gap/></del>, in
         <lb/>quibus <add>de</add> variarum sortium mensuris et casuum fortuitorum proba<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>bilitatibus cum ipso egi. Quod si existimas omnino è ne esse,
         <lb/>ut Dissertationem aliquam Mathematicam Illustrissimis
         <lb/>Dominis <rs key="pers_DE-588-1111043582 pers_DE-588-1178371670 pers_DE-588-1089585993" type="persons">Moderatoribus</rs><note type="editorial">Von 14.10.1713-7.03.1714 waren die Moderatoren der Universität Padua Alvise Pisani (1664-1741), Francesco Loredan (1656-1715), Giovan Francesco  Morosini (1658-1739)</note> offerendam componam, meditabor
         <pb facs="1038283" n="126v"/>
<lb/>argumentum aliquod, quamprimum per otium licuerit. <add>Stipendi<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice></add> <del>Deo</del>
<lb/><subst><del>quantitate stipendium quo expeterem</del><add>m<subst><del>aj</del><add>in</add></subst>us quam qu<unclear>e</unclear> <abbr>D.</abbr> <rs key="pers_DE-588-119112450" type="person">Herma<choice><orig><g ref="#nn">n̄</g></orig><reg>nn</reg></choice>us</rs> gavisus est non</add></subst> expeterem, si Serenissima et Potentissima
         <lb/><rs key="place_GEO-3164603" type="place">Respublica</rs> ad Mathesin docendam me avocaret, <del>qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> rogas, respondeo</del>
<lb/><del>me contentum fore </del>cum et ea qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> ipse pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>stitit
         <lb/><add>Deo <subst><del>val</del><add>fav</add></subst>ente</add> me pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>stiturum<note type="editorial">Wortumstellung: "me pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>stiturum" steht in der vorhergehenden Zeile.</note> confidum. Gratum facies si in quo officia et munia
         <lb/>Professoris Matheseos <add>Patavini</add> consistant significare dignaberis. <rs key="pers_DE-588-118509969" type="person">Patru<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice></rs>
<lb/>meum<del> nonnisi lauti</del> propt<del>r</del>er res domesticas no<choice><orig><g ref="#nn">n̄</g></orig><reg>nn</reg></choice>isi lautissimis con<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>ditionibus alio abiturum credo, cum<subst><del> nuper</del><add> non ita pridem</add></subst> Professionem <subst><del><gap/></del><add><choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice></add></subst> Bata<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>vis honorificis valde et amplis conditionibus sibi oblatam recusaverit.
         <lb/>Ipse <subst><del>cum</del><add>et</add></subst> Adgnat<choice><orig><g ref="#us">[us]</g></orig><reg>us</reg></choice> me<choice><orig><g ref="#us">[us]</g></orig><reg>us</reg></choice> <rs key="pers_DE-588-117589144" type="person">Nicola<choice><orig><g ref="#us">[us]</g></orig><reg>us</reg></choice></rs> multa cum gratiarum actione
         <lb/>Salutem <subst><del>tibi a Te dictam</del><add>plurimam Tibi</add></subst> remittunt.
      </p>
